comments: Barnes (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Schroder's (LAL) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Holmes (SAC) inadvertently makes contact with Harrell's (LAL) face as part of a natural shooting motion.
Schroder (LAL) and Joseph (SAC) engage and disengage with one another off ball.
Harrell (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Joseph's (SAC) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Harrell (LAL) and Joseph (SAC) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Fox (SAC) moves laterally in Schroder's (LAL) path after his gather, and contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Holmes (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Schroder's (LAL) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Kuzma (LAL) maintains legal guarding position as body contact occurs with Fox (SAC) during his driving shot attempt.
Joseph (SAC) briefly places his hand to Kuzma's (LAL) side before correcting.
Fox (SAC) moves underneath Schroder's (LAL) lower body during his shooting motion and contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Joseph (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Morris' (LAL) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Barnes (SAC) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Morris (LAL) brushes Barnes' (SAC) arm and the contact is marginal during his driving shot attempt.
Bjelica (SAC) places his arm to Schroder's (LAL) front during his drive and marginal contact occurs.

Bjelica (SAC) briefly places his hand to Schroder's (LAL) back and marginal contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.  Holmes (SAC) is positioned sideways when he jumps vertically and incidental contact occurs with Schroder after the release of the shot attempt.
Morris (LAL) and Hield (SAC) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Marginal contact occurs as Hield (SAC) and Harrell (LAL) both go for the rebound.
Joseph (SAC) makes contact with Kuzma's (LAL) hand that's on the ball and marginal contact occurs during his shot attempt at the basket.
Barnes (SAC) establishes himself firming up in Caldwell-Pope's (LAL) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Kuzma (LAL) steps out of bounds as he gathers the loose ball.
Horton-Tucker (LAL) commits a take foul on Hield (SAC).
Kuzma (LAL) commits a take foul on Barnes (SAC).
Harrell (LAL) delivers contact to Barnes (SAC) as he sets the screen and the contact affects his ability to defend the play.
Kuzma (LAL) extends his leg as part of a natural shooting motion on the jump shot attempt and the contact with Holmes (SAC) is marginal.
